@node "History"

                                    @{b}History@{ub}

2006.10.31   V1.1    Public release.
                     - Save compared directory history and restore at starting  
                     - Search and display version for binary files
                     - Integrate progress bar and interrupt button in GUI
                     - Integrate new debug system
                     - Some bugs fixed

2006.05.02   V1.0a   Public release.
                     - Fixed bug: Node opening/closing in tree 2 has not effect
                       on the matching node of the 2 other trees

2006.04.29   V1.0    Public release.
                     - First MorphOS/PPC release

@endnode

